# Ownership (always)

Read `AGENTS.md` before editing. One domain per task when possible.

| Domain | Folders |
| --- | --- |
| Persistence | `db/` |
| Frontend | `frontend/` |
| Simulation | `sim/` |
| Owner/GM | `gm/` |
| QA | `qa/` |
| Contracts | `shared/` only |

## Hard rules

- Do not edit another domain's folder unless the user explicitly asks for a cross-domain change.
- Cross-domain communication goes through `shared/` contracts — no sneaking business logic into UI or schema into sim.
- Simulation owns box-score numbers. GM owns front-office intents. Persistence owns saved truth. Frontend owns presentation.
- Prefer invoking the matching skill under `.cursor/skills/` for domain work.
- QA agents review and test; they do not invent product features.
